Title: I Think They Had a Point
Description: October 14
---
I overheard some days talking -- yes, days. I was at first alarmed, as you
 might have been, by what they said.
But then I came to believe they had a point, which wasï¼š
That if they shortened the year by a few months people would have less time
 to worry.
Well, as I already wrote ... I think they had a point? What is your opinion?
